title: Bishoujo Yuugi Unit Crane Game Girls (Crane Game Girls)
synopsis: One day, Saya, an agent of the World Space Association, receives a sudden message that says a large number of asteroids are on a collision course with Earth, and it is her mission to stop them. Unfortunately, the only way to save the Earth is by having three people with extraordinary potential demonstrate a new skill on a crane game, which will create a beam of energy able to divert the asteroids.
related_anime: ['Bishoujo Yuugi Unit Crane Game Girls Galaxy']
